&lt;p>Warriors prepare their burst while waiting for the party buffs to appear.&lt;br>
After the buffs are up, fell cleaves are used first for comfort, but the order of IR GCDs can be swapped around as desired.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="opener-optimization">Opener Optimization&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Assumed Timings:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Tomahawk starts at -0.70s and the pull starts at 0.00s&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Party buffs are expected to be up at around 7.80s, right when the first Inner Chaos goes out.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
